title: SNITCH, MEA TULPA
description:
A Virtually Not Alone Network Event

Pastor Paul Vander Klay brings a Canon to Homeroom, and even the algorithm skips After Socrates #2. In this Livestream, I intend to defile both of the pair of PPs of knowing - with the Salty Snitch, Mea Tulpa. 

If we're lucky, I'll also cover why Kale Zellden can't be my friend anymore. 
Sources (eventually):
@PaulVanderKlay Socrates 3:  /watch?v=y1KtyfEjb9s
JBP clip:  /watch?v=Ubc_xaOczM0

Musics:
Casino courtesy @arcussounds   /watch?v=byfBksff7A4
Agapic Care Agency @the-chris-show /watch?v=hozPGQps0zA
